      • fromHTTPParams

        GenericSetting fromHTTPParams(HashMap<String,String[]> params,
                              int index,
                              String htmlElementID)
        Based on a list of HTTP request form (names & values) and the original value object (of same type/class), parse the later to match the former format with the new values. The original setting will be the object where this function gets called at.
        Parameters:
        params - the new params, and their values, to put into the return object.
        index - the param index where the value is.
        Returns:
        a new GenericSetting with the updated information.
